          {city} properties face {localRisk}. When your insurance company underpays or denies your claim, our NC-licensed public adjusters fight to get you the maximum legal settlement. You pay nothing unless we win.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-10">
          <a href="#claim-form" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-extrabold text-white bg-[#00808C] rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all">
            Free {city} Property Inspection
          </a>
          <a href="tel:3058045489" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-extrabold text-white border-2 border-white/30 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 rounded-xl transition-all">
            📞 (305) 804-5489
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00B5A6]">✓</span> Serving all of {county}</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00B5A6]">✓</span> NC DOI Licensed</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00B5A6]">✓</span> No Recovery, No Fee</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00B5A6]">✓</span> Se habla español</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. LOCAL DAMAGE TYPES (unique per city) -->
  <section class="section-white">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why {city} needs Claim Guardians</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading mb-4">Property Damage Risks Specific to {city} and {county}.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">Insurance companies operating in {county} know these risks — and they train their adjusters to minimize what they pay you. Here's what we fight for.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="card-hover p-8">
